  "keyFeatures": [
    "Single Vagrantfile workflow for reproducible dev environments",
    "Multi-provider support: VirtualBox, VMware, Docker, HyperV, AWS",
    "Built-in provisioning with Shell, Ansible, Chef, Puppet, Docker, Salt",
    "Flexible networking: port forwarding, private and public networks",
    "Synced folders via NFS, SMB, rsync, or VirtualBox shared folders",
    "Rich plugin system for commands, providers, provisioners, and more",
    "Multi-machine environments from a single Vagrantfile",
    "Vagrant Cloud for box distribution and discovery",
    "Snapshot support for saving and restoring machine state",
    "Cross-platform: Windows, macOS, and Linux"
